arStrings.szText: “I found this rune on the ground. Do you know what it is?”
Huh. Vaults are full of those things. Folk brought 'em to town, and now there's demons in their heads. Look at the markings! Mage clans—bad luck!
You wanna help? Get that thing out of town, put it back where it came from! Vault’s north of here.
